{"tid":2282864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛 民 前 議 員 見 字 速 全 體 去 美 國","createTime":"2020-11-12T06:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T07:09:47.000Z","uid":151057,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"654e5f74ec493a1e98a566d5244c5a0950812418","tid":2282864,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"如果你哋係出於愛香港而做議員<br />\n你哋宜家就係最好嘅機會一洗過去留戀議席嘅歪風<br />\n你哋已經再冇退路 香港政治機器冇你哋嘅位<br />\n但係海外戰線極需要你哋<br />\n<br />\n黃之峰可以製造到咁大個美國戰線並唔係因為佢有咩才智過人<br />\n而係識得善用佢嘅香港民主抗爭者代表身份<br />\n<br />\n你哋作為被流放前民選議員<br />\n你哋可以做嘅事甚至係開創一條全新嘅民主議會國際戰線<br />\n去代表香港人向各國政府發言<br />\n可以去拉撤各國民主國會議員<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋跳出舒適圈<br />\n你哋可以改變到香港未來<br />\n<br />\n去美國啦 唔好再留係香港<br />\n唔好做白頭佬二號<br />\n唔通等有朝一日民主派前議員大圍捕先明白自己嘅角色嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重覆一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民間議會"},{"pid":"f04d23af17fe29a3ebe720639a30badeb1215896","tid":2282864,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a231dad2d969131da21b3aae107d5dfa800d573e","tid":2282864,"uid":275623,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"鳩嗡真係易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ca747a71006a67d2529cbe60a0c961f59aba3b","tid":2282864,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"534e82228ab63262a86f966417c3ab4b50abb169","tid":2282864,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:09:47.000Z","msg":"走到既即走，<br />\n之後會用國安法拉d議員，<br />\n乜鳩都話犯左國安法"}]}